Template Smartcash Community Vote Proposal – MYCE widget integration

1.	Proposal Name
SmartNode hosting web-widget integration [MYCE Team]

2.	Summary
Allowing Smartcash owners to enjoy their rewards, monitor their nodes without worrying on how to install and update their masternode.
The widget we are presenting here allows for Smartcash users to have a guide on hosting without enforcing them to pay to use it.
In simple words it helps Smartcash’s adoption.

