- MYCE web widget 
We have developed https://www.myce.world/testing-widget as a widget for websites. It allows for users to have a guide on hosting without enforcing them to pay to use it. 
In clear the MYCE widget will come with the following features:
Available NOW
- free masternode hosting guide 
- free monitoring
- MYCE masternode hosting solution 10$ per month payable in BTC 

What is Coming after?
- Go from $BTC directly into a masternode without going through the hassle of exchanges.
 From $BTC > $SMART node running on same place
- Customer support regardless users being our client or not
- Discord integration
- Accept payments in SmartCash Telegram / Web / Discord 
(what do you mean exactly, hosting payable in $SMART or users can pay our solution from Smartcash telegram,discord,web?)
